    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that feels like such a lie. like just pretending to care about \"moments\" just to distract myself from the fact that nothing matters. it’s exhausting to keep performing this role of being a \"person\" when the universe is just cold and indifferent. it feels like we're just fighting a losing battle against the inevitable.",
